    <div class="main review-item" id="4889194">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4889194/" class="title-link">这个道在世界各地均受到尊崇</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4889194"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/49989056/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u49989056-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/49989056/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">公益霎哈嘉瑜伽</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-04-02"
      class="main-meta">2011-04-02 13:40:39</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4889194_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  中国古代曾经有过很伟大的哲人，中国人相信孔子的人文主义，但是另外一个很重要的便是老子，老子是降世的大宗师。老子曾经描述过扬子江(长江)，我也到过扬子江去。老子所讲的「道」，其实就是我们讲的 Kundalini，灵性的能量。老子是个诗人，他所描述的方式是很隐晦，很微妙的...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4889194_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4889194_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



